VALUES ('8f1a9204-8c45-4ae0-aff4-7b8fef13faf5', '32', NULL, 'i - s imposed at any other criminal provision, except', 'penal_code', 'en', '.- Deyences and conviction by default In the event of a default conviction, the forfeiture is incurred to start from the day of the completion of the advertising measures provided for by the Code of Criminal Procedure. .  General : Service or Achier Legislatie Er  co IT A Cé section Other AC penalties');
